        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer34857425" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer41483115258019179">James Tiptree Jr. wrote short stories like a goddamned <i>ninja</i>. Each of these well-selected pieces feel perfectly machined, a clockwork of unknowable complexity and beauty. There is humor, sadness, and stunning beauty here, as well as moments of utter darkness, Tipree has stared into the void, and it permeates her worldview and her voice.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


