  <span id="freeText17955687810281256584" style="display:none">A collection of short stories &amp; novellas from Alice Sheldon aka James Tiptree Jr.<br /><br />This is not an easy book. The settings are really alien, but Alice does not stop to explain. I felt that even the text reads differently. But I don't regret the effort at all.<br /><br />This book has both the principles of a humorous and sad book. It was dark, but truly written beautifully. The short stories were impressive. There were many ideas that a person could spend their life looking over. This book definitely required re-read to understand it completely.<br /><br />Actual Ratings:- ⭐⭐⭐⭐ and Half Stars</span>
