        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1301827282" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4430876166453866005">Read these all again to discuss them with Luke on the SFBRP podcast! As great as ever. Please see my <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/271276722' rel='nofollow noopener'>previous review</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText4430876166453866005" style="display:none">Read these all again to discuss them with Luke on the SFBRP podcast! As great as ever. Please see my <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/271276722" rel="nofollow noopener">previous review</a>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4430876166453866005" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

